data.description: Welcome to Four Palms! Four Royal Palm trees stand majestically in the Florida sky as you enjoy the great views across the water to the beautiful Copper Creek Clubhouse and Recreation Center. Nestled in the heart of the desirable Copper Creek subdivision, this four-bedroom, three-bath home has the desirable Great Room layout of the popular “Brook” model from the Signature Collection. Water views abound from the Great Room, Dining Room, Primary Bedroom, Kitchen, and Lanai. Master-Planned Bliss: Copper Creek is more than a neighborhood; it's a lifestyle. Immerse yourself in this thoughtfully designed community of homes tailored for modern living. Adjacent to the renowned St. Lucie County Public School Allapattah Flats K-8, with easy access to shopping, dining, and recreation. Amenities Galore: Enjoy resort-style living with a community clubhouse, sparkling pool, tennis courts, basketball courts, a fitness center, and a tot lot. Every day feels like a vacation! Photos are virtually staged
